Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Project Summary", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.755274163607428*^9, 
  3.755274166357678*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"c88a169e-ce9c-4f7b-ba47-\
d24797bedfdc"],

Cell[TextData[{
 "This project is composed of three efforts\n1) Propagation in various \
scenarios\n2) A study of optical image processing via 4-",
 StyleBox["f",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " imaging system\n3) Optical Fourier transforms -- The SPIFI technique\n\n\
Ultimately the goal of this project is to provide students with experience in \
wave propagation, optical image filtering, and a basic understanding of the \
SPIFI technique."
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.7552741528068542`*^9, 3.75527415801682*^9}, {
   3.7552742810456867`*^9, 3.755274291135635*^9}, {3.755274408601207*^9, 
