Cell["\<\
The deliverable for this project is working code and documentation \
articulating the results. The results are three-fold:
1. Propagation simulation mayhem: see required plots below
2. 4-f spatial filter for optical image processing: see required plots below
3. Simulating SPIFI \
\>", "Text",
