   ImageSize->{872.5875000000001, Automatic},
   ImageSizeRaw->{2138, 1268},
   PlotRange->{{0, 2138}, {0, 1268}}]], "Text",ExpressionUUID->
  "88921ad8-fbab-49ca-a168-dd80d4fe7467"],
 "\n",
 StyleBox["Figure waveguide coupling simulation:",
  FontWeight->"Bold"],
 " The figure shows the wave resolved propagation of a focusing Gaussian beam \
coupled into a hollow waveguide. Notice that the wavefronts of the wave \
remain FLAT after they enter the waveguide. This is the principal action of \
waveguide and causes the wave to stay confined.\n",
 StyleBox["\n1) What is the optimal value of ",
  FontSize->13],
 Cell[BoxData[
  SubscriptBox["w", "0"]],ExpressionUUID->
  "ef192e1b-6faf-4f08-9cf9-fa9de406d65c"],
 " i.e., the size of the beam radius at the capillary input that maximizes \
the energy entering the capillary?"
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.760653317870872*^9, 3.760653379482809*^9}, {
